Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when I have a miraculous battle over a crow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,with Black Phantom Thief, \Nan unexpected rival, what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'll just say this to you once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you come in contact with the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's the scene of a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never be arrogant. Never underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See into their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give undivided concentration \Nto your fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last advice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use every trick you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, never lose \Nyour smile or dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...remember your poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:51.51,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,15,,{\a1}{\fad(0,100)}Midnight Crow (Part One): \NThe Name is Corbeau the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came prepared with two \Nmore back-up plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:44.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, Hakuba took a leave \Nof absence to travel abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:48.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with Inspector Nakamori \Nin bed with a bad cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this is a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's biggest black diamond,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Midnight Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to pick this lock\N in less than a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands aren't moving the way I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's really cold in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:15.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...has a weakness to cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba and Inspector?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You let down your guard because you \Nthought I was home sick in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My cop nature kicked that cold\N to the curb after a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only told Aoko I had a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Kid know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! I'm not Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:32.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're Oshima from Squad C!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid put a mask of you on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a-and escaped out the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, what should I do about these handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Figure something out yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My double disguise worked like a charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting one of the investigators to sleep\N just in case was the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like I'll have to reschedule \Nto get another shot at that jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba's watching it like a hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what the inspector said bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:25.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the plan go smoothly for the \Ninspector tonight because of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying in Kid's outfit in these circumstances\N could be easily misconstrued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please change into something else right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:54.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, did you see the news on the net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Complete Defeat \Nfor Kid the Phantom Thief"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers and jeers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who toasts with ginger ale?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why do you have band-aids \Nall over your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The price I paid for using strong adhesive \Non that second mask so it wouldn't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, Jii-chan, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:28.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there's an old man \Ngiving advice to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Senior Adviser Suzuki \Ndoesn't have anything to do with this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that rich old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Harry Nezu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a famous magic trick buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It says the police drove Kid off this time\N thanks to Nezu-san's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic trick buster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. His nickname's "the Hedgehog."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He made his name debunking \Nfraudulent spirit mediums.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems magicians all over the world regularly \Nchallenge him, but are soon "busted."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This says he's coming to Japan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:09.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe the old man's going \Nto meet Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is a gift for the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate driving Kid away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna meet somebody famous, so you \Nwant him to have a little style, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in Japan to help \Narrest Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief... \NThe brat in the white suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat? I've been on his trail for 18 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a youngster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even his name is "Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fancy necktie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a present from my daughter's friend, to \Ncelebrate us driving away Kid the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your daughter has a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'd say he has bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the advance notice was for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I was afraid he'd realized there's a \Ncamera and mic planted in the tie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he sent it to the police \Ndepartment two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,saying he was going to try again \Ntonight at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And does he know you're going to change \Nthe exhibition room of the jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I went out of my way to \Nannounce it on TV last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he knows \Nthe exact room, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just have to wait for him \Nto show up, as brazen as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the mousetrap I've prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Minus 10 degrees Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this floor that cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was my instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we really be able \Nto catch him like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll work for the brat in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He got away last time \Nbecause it wasn't cold enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:08.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deceiving the eyes with skilled fingers \Nis what a magician does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A phantom thief who uses magic becomes a \Nbabe in the woods if he can't use those fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures they would go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it's also hard for us cops \Nto catch Kid in this cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your bodies will be too \Nsluggish from the cold to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay toasty-warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:37.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll just sneak into the building before \Nmidnight, impersonate that old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less \Nabout that brat in white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we make it this cold\N in order to catch Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:52.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prey isn't the one in white...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the one in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, my father, the commissioner, \Nreceived another advance notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tonight at midnight, please forgive \Nmy rudeness when I take my black jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Corbeau the Phantom Thief"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Corbeau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Corbeau" means crow in French.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he refers to the \NMidnight Crow as "his."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And crows do like shiny objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I received the same missive last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why I've come \Nto my father's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:36.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But who is this Corbeau?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A phantom thief who's been \Nactive in Las Vegas lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scattering countless crow feathers \Nat the scene of the crime is his M.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the surprising thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is that he looks just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A black feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the outfit, my guess is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're a fan of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's changing his voice, but it feels like\N I've heard it before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I have a feeling\N I've seen you once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:01.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've devoted yourself to thieving in Japan \Nwhile cosplaying in an outfit like my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Child the Robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've only just started being active!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's copying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffered from an illness \Nfor quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After healing up, I was just \Nwaiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting to take revenge for my \Nfellow apprentice, Kuroba Toichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who was murdered eight years ago\N at a magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:42.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I repurposed this stage outfit\N he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from your aping the style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:52.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, it seems you've got \Nportable heating pads stuck all over your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:56.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so the fact that you're about to dive \Ninto a trap prepared by that hedgehog
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,tells me you're a thoughtless lightweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we make a wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:12.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight I intend to melt into the darkness,\N hiding all traces of myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and then make that black jewel, the Midnight \NCrow, my own, without even touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you can't understand how I did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to be a good sport and \Nretire as a professional thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:31.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for two ghosts\N of Kuroba Toichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if I see through \Nyour trick, then {\i1}you{\i0} retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two phantom thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, no matter how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to take the jewel \Nfrom the one who steals it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stone of Life... Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kid's not coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you got that mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:31.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It just came to the department. \NIt said, "Tonight, I'll just be watching."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was rerouted through an overseas server, \Nso we couldn't pinpoint the original sender,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the mail had Kid's usual trademark, \Nso we believe it really came from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's curious about \NCorbeau the Phantom Thief, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Corbeau, Corvette, whatever, he's \Nthrown cold water on the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we've lost \Nthe chance to catch Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's no need to touch that pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pedestal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in my country and \Nhad it brought here to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my secret weapon against Corbeau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, it looks like \Nan ordinary pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I release the safety like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if there are any objects nearby, \Nsharp blades spring out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:17:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it rotates at a high speed \Nthat can rip anything to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the case is \Nmade of ultra-dense glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the black fabric \Nthe jewel lies upon is engineered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to be stab-proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:32.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is the genuine black \Ndiamond, the Midnight Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That case has a weird contraption, \Nbut it's not locked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori, the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to wear a gas mask\N and sit atop this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,holding on to the handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you hold on to those handles,\N the case can't be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori! It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Corbeau the Phantom Thief,\N you night bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear from anywhere you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:26.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be the one sitting on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,F-From the ceiling vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow feathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Corbeau is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die before I let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about the jewel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I held on the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in its place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A word etched into it... Corbeau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he do it without opening the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That really is magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the time to be impressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are words on the bottom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time I'll be back \Nto take the real thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The real thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:20:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a trick I often pull \Nin my confrontations with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a strange foreboding, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I switched it out with a fake \Nright before the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:14.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it seems he saw through \Nmy bait-and-switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, even if it was a fake, \Nhe really did steal the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we don't know how he did it,\N maybe next time, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main point is that our field of vision \Nwas obscured by those crow feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being distracted by that was our downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we can't afford to neglect \Nthe ventilation shafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get this coin over to the crime lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm sure he won't have \Nleft his fingerprints on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He melted into the darkness, \Nerasing all traces of himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and stole the jewel without touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is no time to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he take the jewel \Nwithout opening the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was magic, there would've been some \Ndevice in the case, covered by the black cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also curious about his identity, \Nsince he called Dad his "fellow apprentice".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jii-chan said he can't recall \Nanyone referring to Dad by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I'll head home \Nand search the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The lights are on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaito! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An unexpected person showed up, \Nbut this is no time to be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna settle my showdown \Nwith Corbeau the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The illusion must go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I think I'll relax \Nand do this final preview alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Corbeau the Phantom Thief... \NHow the heck did he do that trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he picked a fight with me \Nshows just how strong he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't be defeated here \Nand have a good reason for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:52.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight Crow (Part Two): \NClash! White or Black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The last episode! "Midnight Crow (Part Two): \NClash! White or Black?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the last illusion!
